data.description: Welcome home to this stunning brick ranch located just outside the village of Bethel. With convenience to 125 and 32, you can feel close to everything without being in the hustle and bustle. Situated on a half-acre, this fenced in beauty will fit all of your needs! Updated laminate flooring throughout and a new HVAC system and HWH in 2022! Enjoy every season in your sunroom along with family functions in your spacious formal dining room.
